				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Leveling solo past 27<a name="65205"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 30 04 8:05 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>When you are charm kiting with the level 27 song, I found it best to have your pet targetted most or all of the time.  Make the following 2-line Hotkey...
<br />

<br />
/pet attack
<br />
/pet target
<br />

<br />
Charm your pet... target his prey... hit this key...
<br />
pet goes in to attack and you immediately retarget it.
<br />
pet break charm after third tick  re-charm... toggle targets... hit the key... repeat
<br />

<br />
When your pet or his prey are low health.. bellow down to death.. chant down once you get level 30 
<br />

<br />
same technique works nicely for swarming, the most beat down survivor is always my pet</span></td>
